select m.multiframeid,sum(tablerows) from Multiframe as m, MultiframeDetector as mfd where m.multiframeID=mfd.multiframeID and project like 'atlas' and frameType like 'stack' group by m.multiframeid order by sum(tableRows) desc  /*select  * from atlasDetection  where multiframeID=158148 and ra>0*/

select   s.ra as raDeg,s.dec as decDeg,gAperMag3,rAperMag3,x,y,s.framesetid from atlasSource as s, atlasMergeLog as l, atlasDetection as d where  l.frameSetID=s.frameSetID and gmfid >0 and rmfid >0 and ( (gapermag3 between 0 and 22 and rapermag3 <0 and gSeqNum=d.seqNum and geNum=d.extnum and gmfid=d.multiframeID) /* (rapermag3 between 0 and 22 and gapermag3 <0 and rSeqNum=d.seqNum and reNum=d.extnum and rmfid=d.multiframeID)*/ )
select * from Filter

SELECT     distinct             mi.arcfile as i_name,             mg.arcfile as g_name,             mi.filterID as i_file,             mg.filterID as g_filt  FROM       atlasSource as a,            atlasMergeLog as l,            multiframeDetector as dg,            multiframeDetector as di,            multiframe as mg,            multiframe as mi  WHERE     a.framesetid=l.framesetid AND             l.gmfid=dg.multiframeid AND             l.imfid=di.multiframeid AND             l.geNum=dg.extNum AND             l.ieNum=di.extNum AND             dg.multiframeid=mg.multiframeid AND             di.multiframeid=mi.multiframeid AND             mi.filterID=2 AND             mg.filterID=4 AND             a.gAperMag3 > 0.0 AND             a.iAperMag3 > 0.0 AND             (a.priOrSec=0 OR a.priOrSec=a.frameSetID)

SELECT     distinct            mi.arcfile as i_name,            mg.arcfile as g_name,            mi.filterID as i_file,            mg.filterID as g_filt  FROM       atlasSource as a,            atlasMergeLog as l,            multiframeDetector as dg,            multiframeDetector as di,            multiframe as mg,            multiframe as mi  WHERE      a.framesetid=l.framesetid AND            l.gmfid=dg.multiframeid AND            l.imfid=di.multiframeid AND            l.geNum=dg.extNum AND            l.ieNum=di.extNum AND            dg.multiframeid=mg.multiframeid AND            di.multiframeid=mi.multiframeid AND            mi.filterID=4 AND            mg.filterID=2 AND            a.gAperMag3 > 0.0 AND            a.iAperMag3 > 0.0 AND            (a.priOrSec=0 OR a.priOrSec=a.frameSetID)

SELECT     neighbours.distanceMins FROM     atlassourcexDR8photoobj AS neighbours,     (     SELECT TOP 10         sourceId AS ident     FROM         atlasSource     ) AS sources WHERE     neighbours.masterObjID - sources.ident < 1000000
